# NETWORK::NETWORK_IS_IN_PLATFORM_PARTY

## Summary
Sends an session invite to all members of the platform party

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Hardcoded to return false.
